Important information

Safety Information:
Keep cap tightly closed after use

Directions:
Apply a neat stroke on the upper eyelid. It is recommended to start from the inner corner of the eye and move outwards for best results. You can use the smudger at the other end to create a smokey look.

Product description

Colour:Deep Black New

Accentuate the beauty of your eyes with the Lakme Eyeconic Kajal. This dermatologically tested kajal is just what you need for completing your eye makeup or carrying a simple, only-kajal look. It's a smudge proof, water proof kajal and can add the dramatic and glamorous look to your eyes. It has intense matte texture for Eyeconic eyes. You can Experiment with a thin line or a bold wing, this kajal is great for day and night looks. Its long-lasting- up to 22 hours without smudging and is completely water proof. It is designed with an easy to use and convenient twist-up format. Just one stroke of the Lakme Eyeconic Kajal enhances your simple look to a more stylish avatar. Its beat all your timelines, be it meetings, travelling or just a day out and lasts for 22 hrs. You are incomplete without kajal and this is a perfect everyday product! Get the Lakme Eyeconic Kajal in black, now. The Eyeconic goes best with your Eyeconic mascara. To enhance your eyes further. You can also use from our 4 eye quartet pallets to enhance your eye to wedding a wedding, party and work look. Draw a neat stroke on the upper lid, starting from the inner corner of the eyes, extending outwards. Repeat on the lower lid.

4.0 out of 5 starsPerfectly Safe, Easy Application, But, Not The Darkest Black!
6 August 2018
Colour: Deep Black NewVerified Purchase
Gifting for your loved ones can be really an issue if you do it on a continuous basis and will slowly run out of options. However, Amazon never fails to amaze us and that is how it ends up putting a smile on each one's face. Lakme Eyeconic was a gift to a very long friend of mine as I knew her choice. The review is based on her perception of usage and my view on her face after application.

The highlights of the product are:

1) Perfectly Safe - The Kajal is perfectly safe to apply without any irritation whatsoever. This is one of the major reason one prefers it above its peers. It does not irritate even a bit and quite comfortable to apply on.

2) Not That Long Lasting - It lasts for quite long, but not for 22 hours as mentioned. However, one having oily skin will tend to find it smudgy after a while. It is needless to mention that the kajal is waterproof.

3) Bold Patches - The eyelids and lashes are given a great look and it looks really good. I have seen my friend transforming instantly after the application!

4) Not The Blackest Despite having the item name as Deep Black, it is not really the black most kajal in the market. I have had gifted Colossal Kajal to her which is quite darker than this one.

5) Convenient and Portable Stick The kajal comes in a retractable twist mechanism which is quite helpful and a strong cap locking makes it perfectly safe and portable to carry on.

I have had bought this for 150 rupees, but, now it is being listed at 135 rupees. Keep added the item to the wishlist and you will be notified of a price drop, if any!
